Tezdel tyaẓiḍt.
Zeddlent tyuẓaḍ.
Turew-d tyaẓiḍt tamellalt.
Ur yeḥmil ara timellalin.
Ur teḥmil ara ad tečč timellalin.
Iḥemmel timellalin yewwan deg waman.
Iḥemmel timellalin di zzit.
Ur itett ara timellalin.
Acimi ur ttetteḍ ara timellalin?
Timellalin n tyuẓaḍ n tmurt ifent tid n tyuẓaḍ n trisiti.
Tameṭṭut-is d taneɛmart.
Tameṭṭut-is mačči d timexlit.

